Attribution — derived from mpump
──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

mpumpit embeds and reuses the audio engine of "mpump — Instant browser
groovebox", Copyright (C) 2024-2026 gdamdam (https://github.com/gdamdam),
which is licensed under the GNU Affero General Public License, version 3.0
only.

Because mpumpit is a derivative work of mpump's AGPL-3.0-only engine, mpumpit
as a whole is distributed under the same license (AGPL-3.0-only). The engine
code is NOT relicensed.

The following files are copied verbatim (apart from import-path adjustments and
an added license header) from mpump's source tree (mpump/server/):

  src/engine/AudioPort.ts      ← src/engine/AudioPort.ts
  src/engine/drumSynth.ts      ← src/engine/drumSynth.ts
  src/engine/CVOutput.ts       ← src/engine/CVOutput.ts
  src/engine/storage.ts        ← src/utils/storage.ts
  src/engine/soundPresets.ts   ← src/data/soundPresets.ts
  public/worklets/*.js         ← public/worklets/*.js
    (poly-synth, moog-filter, diode-filter, bitcrusher,
     sync-osc, fm-osc, wavetable-osc)

The following file is derived (trimmed to the engine-relevant subset) from
mpump:

  src/engine/types.ts          ← src/types.ts (synth/drum/effect types only)

All other files (the MIDI input router, the SoundModule facade, the drum
compatibility map, persistence, and the UI) are original to mpumpit and are
likewise licensed AGPL-3.0-only.

